name: Drip Coffee
description: The traditional method of brewing where hot water slowly passes through grounds.

name: Dark Roast
description: A full-bodied dark roast with smoky undertones for those who like it strong.

name: Classic Espresso
description: A concentrated shot of coffee served in a small cup. Rich and intense.

name: Americano
description: Espresso diluted with hot water. Similar strength to brewed coffee but different flavor.

name: Cappuccino
description: Equal parts espresso, steamed milk, and milk foam.

name: Flat White
description: Espresso with microfoam (steamed milk with fine bubbles).

name: Classic Latte
description: Espresso with plenty of steamed milk and a thin layer of foam.

name: Vanilla Latte
description: Classic latte with rich vanilla syrup.

name: Caramel Latte
description: Espresso and milk sweetened with caramel syrup.

name: Mocha
description: Espresso mixed with rich chocolate syrup and steamed milk.

name: Earl Grey
description: Classic British black tea flavored with oil of bergamot.

name: Green Tea
description: Steamed green tea leaves rich in antioxidants.

name: Chai Tea Latte
description: Black tea spiced with cinnamon and cardamom mixed with steamed milk.

name: Cold Brew
description: Coffee steeped in cold water for 24 hours for a smooth low-acid taste.

name: Nitro Cold Brew
description: Cold brew infused with nitrogen gas for a creamy texture.

name: Iced Latte
description: Espresso and cold milk served over ice.

name: Hot Chocolate
description: Steamed milk with rich chocolate sauce and whipped cream.

name: Red Eye
description: Regular drip coffee topped with a shot of espresso for extra caffeine.

name: Honey Lavender Latte
description: Latte infused with honey and lavender syrup.

name: Iced Tea Lemonade
description: Half iced black tea half lemonade.
